{"tid":1140974,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載] 學歷差太多真的會有溝通問題","createTime":"2019-05-06T07:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T13:27:04.000Z","uid":5866,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd96a7f64265f7019d7beca0a784d8e6e7bb994","tid":1140974,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:29:29.000Z","msg":"這的確是實話啊<br />\n<br />\n尤其如果是情侶之間的話更有感<br />\n<br />\n我講幾個低學歷都會有的現象<br />\n<br />\n語意不清：講話不清楚很難溝通，不知道是字彙量不多還是怎樣，常常支支吾吾的<br />\n<br />\n情緒波動大：可能上一秒還很開心，結果下一秒就直接開始哭鬧，解決問題只會用叫跟哭，而且公共場所也一樣完全不顧其他人的感受<br />\n<br />\n固執：很難溝通，完全聽不下其他人的意見，邏輯直接關機無視別人說什麼，搭配上面那一點真的毀天滅地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三分鐘熱度：一開始興致勃勃，可是一遇到困難就放棄，常常只是因為想要就要求別人買，但用了幾次以後就丟著了，浪費<br />\n<br />\n哀<br />\n<br />\n不只這些<br />\n<br />\n這些只是其中一部分而已<br />\n<br />\n但是她真的很可愛<br />\n<br />\n所以我們男生還是多讓讓女孩吧<br />\n<br />\n希望她之後上小學會有所改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1556081082.A.48D.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1556081082.A.48D.html&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=90a91f34\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1556081082.A.48D.html</a>"},{"pid":"960df2d03660def1178a2c4fc5454612e1b877ea","tid":1140974,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa2599dc00f54f50546c2557448c2e4905ba5fa","tid":1140974,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T07:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/117063880/original.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F117063880